[
    {
        "text": "“Can you move just a\nlittle bit to this way?",
        "start": 0.078,
        "duration": 2.377
    },
    {
        "text": "Perfect.”",
        "start": 2.455,
        "duration": 1.457
    },
    {
        "text": "“A-L-L-I-A, my name\nis Allia Phillips.",
        "start": 3.912,
        "duration": 7.148
    },
    {
        "text": "I am 10 years old.",
        "start": 11.06,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "I live in New York, New York.",
        "start": 13.78,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "And I live in a shelter.",
        "start": 17.46,
        "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
        "text": "And I love playing violin.",
        "start": 19.11,
        "duration": 3.264
    },
    {
        "text": "OK, I’m going to have\nto stand up for this.",
        "start": 26.064,
        "duration": 3.486
    },
    {
        "text": "A lot of things are really\nhappening right now,",
        "start": 29.55,
        "duration": 3.98
    },
    {
        "text": "like Covid-19.",
        "start": 33.53,
        "duration": 2.352
    },
    {
        "text": "[Violin playing]",
        "start": 35.882,
        "duration": 2.888
    },
    {
        "text": "I’ve heard that it is\na very contagious virus.",
        "start": 38.77,
        "duration": 5.66
    },
    {
        "text": "And when people get it,\na lot of people",
        "start": 44.43,
        "duration": 2.79
    },
    {
        "text": "have to go to the hospital.",
        "start": 47.22,
        "duration": 1.17
    },
    {
        "text": "But some of them\nhave to get isolated.",
        "start": 48.39,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s changed my life",
        "start": 53.58,
        "duration": 2.39
    },
    {
        "text": "because now, we don’t\nget to go in school.",
        "start": 55.97,
        "duration": 3.63
    },
    {
        "text": "My teacher told\nus that she didn’t",
        "start": 59.6,
        "duration": 2.57
    },
    {
        "text": "know if it was going to\nclose for the whole year.",
        "start": 62.17,
        "duration": 4.45
    },
    {
        "text": "Ta-da.”",
        "start": 66.62,
        "duration": 1.503
    },
    {
        "text": "“You’ve got blanky fuzz\nin your hair.",
        "start": 68.665,
        "duration": 2.405
    },
    {
        "text": "Right now, me and\nAllia are actually",
        "start": 71.07,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "living in a family shelter.”",
        "start": 73.47,
        "duration": 2.442
    },
    {
        "text": "“I don’t like the\nway you brush it.",
        "start": 75.912,
        "duration": 1.458
    },
    {
        "text": "You brush it so hard.",
        "start": 77.37,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "Basically, it’s one room\nwith a bathroom,",
        "start": 79.17,
        "duration": 4.17
    },
    {
        "text": "and then one bed\nand a bunk bed.",
        "start": 83.34,
        "duration": 3.21
    },
    {
        "text": "I guess, it’s now\nmy classroom, too.”",
        "start": 86.55,
        "duration": 2.831
    },
    {
        "text": "“I got contacted by her\nschool to go pick up",
        "start": 91.655,
        "duration": 2.645
    },
    {
        "text": "her iPad device.",
        "start": 94.3,
        "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
        "text": "And her iPad does\nnot have internet.",
        "start": 95.95,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "The shelter that we’re in,\nthey do not allow internet.",
        "start": 98.77,
        "duration": 3.945
    },
    {
        "text": "What classroom stuff are\nwe going to do today?",
        "start": 102.715,
        "duration": 3.315
    },
    {
        "text": "Math?”",
        "start": 106.03,
        "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
        "text": "“Well, science is\nalready too hard.",
        "start": 107.11,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "It keeps on pausing\nitself, just freezing.”",
        "start": 109.12,
        "duration": 4.38
    },
    {
        "text": "“Oh OK, I will look into\nthat in a little bit.”",
        "start": 113.5,
        "duration": 3.765
    },
    {
        "text": "“Across the room.”",
        "start": 117.265,
        "duration": 1.03
    },
    {
        "text": "“And see what’s going on.",
        "start": 118.295,
        "duration": 2.225
    },
    {
        "text": "I have a cellphone.",
        "start": 120.52,
        "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
        "text": "We use the hot spot.",
        "start": 122.38,
        "duration": 1.59
    },
    {
        "text": "I don’t have a lot of data.",
        "start": 123.97,
        "duration": 1.17
    },
    {
        "text": "And it’s a little\nspotty and slow.",
        "start": 125.14,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Essentially, that’s\njust where we’ve",
        "start": 127.9,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "been is puttering outside to\nget a better signal, hoping",
        "start": 129.82,
        "duration": 4.77
    },
    {
        "text": "it gets better.”",
        "start": 134.59,
        "duration": 2.205
    },
    {
        "text": "“A school has 17 tables\nin the cafeteria.",
        "start": 136.795,
        "duration": 4.815
    },
    {
        "text": "Each table has 12 seats.”",
        "start": 141.61,
        "duration": 3.3
    },
    {
        "text": "“I am worried that children\nare going to get left behind",
        "start": 144.91,
        "duration": 3.57
    },
    {
        "text": "because they don’t\nhave their devices",
        "start": 148.48,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "or they didn’t have the\naccess to the internet.",
        "start": 150.25,
        "duration": 3.09
    },
    {
        "text": "Let’s try that one again.”",
        "start": 153.34,
        "duration": 2.115
    },
    {
        "text": "“So we’ll probably have\nto redo our whole grade,",
        "start": 155.455,
        "duration": 3.735
    },
    {
        "text": "and relearn everything\nwe already know.”",
        "start": 159.19,
        "duration": 3.15
    },
    {
        "text": "“Right now, my biggest\nworry for Allia",
        "start": 165.46,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "would be the\nsocial interaction.",
        "start": 168.19,
        "duration": 3.9
    },
    {
        "text": "My mother, who’s disabled,\nand her service animal",
        "start": 172.09,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "lives with us.",
        "start": 174.85,
        "duration": 0.98
    },
    {
        "text": "So we’re all in this\nreally tiny space.”",
        "start": 175.83,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "“Yeah.",
        "start": 178.67,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m worried about that",
        "start": 179.17,
        "duration": 0.99
    },
    {
        "text": "because my grandmother,\nshe is really old.",
        "start": 180.16,
        "duration": 3.8
    },
    {
        "text": "And if she gets it or\nif my mother gets sick,",
        "start": 183.96,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "they could get hurt.",
        "start": 186.28,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "And if they both get it,\nwho’s going to take care of me",
        "start": 188.05,
        "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
        "text": "that day?",
        "start": 191.29,
        "duration": 2.65
    },
    {
        "text": "And then if we’re all\nlocked in the same room,",
        "start": 193.94,
        "duration": 2.15
    },
    {
        "text": "how are we going to be safe?”",
        "start": 196.09,
        "duration": 4.262
    }
]